Installations (Plugins)
1. breaking space
2. yaml
3. Kubernetes
4. kubernetes support
5. mini kube -> https://adamtheautomator.com/install-virtualbox-on-windows-10/

==============================================
1. pod
    A pod is one or more container (A running docker image)
2. Pod - Gets wrapped into a Replica Set
    (It controls the number of ports e.g replicates the running Pod)
3. Replica Set Gets wrapped into a Deployment

4. All this gets wrapped in a yaml file

==============================================
INSTALL MINI Kube
        https://minikube.sigs.k8s.io/docs/start/
1. winget install minikube

INSTALL VirtualBox 
2.  https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads
============= IF YOU DON'T WANT TO INSTALL ANYTHING THEN FOLLOW ONLINE================
1. https://training.play-with-kubernetes.com/
======================================


======================================
1. Start Mini Kube
   - minikube start
   - minikube start --driver=virtualbox
   - minikube start --no-vtx-check
   - minikube start --driver=virtualbox --no-vtx-check
   - minikube start --driver=docker
   - minikube start --driver=hyperv

2. Run or deploy a pod
    kubectl create -f pod.yaml

